<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN" class="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>KY · src 本地测试</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/css/main.css">
  <style>
    .ky-test { max-width: 720px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1.25rem; }
    .ky-test h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .ky-test .sub { color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .ky-test .row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; margin: 0.75rem 0; }
    .ky-test select { min-width: 12rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--text-primary); }
    .ky-test button { padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--primary-600); background: var(--primary-600); color: #fff; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
    .ky-test button.secondary { background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--text-primary); border-color: var(--border-color); }
    .ky-test pre { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 4rem; }
    .ky-test .hint { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 0.35rem; }
    /* 避免结果区大色块在部分浏览器层叠下挡住上方按钮 */
    .ky-test .row { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .ky-test .results-section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="ky-test">
    <h1>KY 开源包 · <code>src</code> 模块测试</h1>
    <p class="sub">请双击运行 <code>启动测试.bat</code>，用 HTTP 打开本页（<code>file://</code> 无法加载 ES 模块 / fetch <code>data/</code>）。</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">免税州样例包 · taxfree-preview-pack.js</h2>
    <p class="hint">地址来自 <code>data/tf-preview.pack.json</code>。<strong>电话规则与主站 <code>generateUSAddress</code> 一致</strong>：从 <code>usRegions</code>（默认 <code>data/addr-regions-us.json</code>）里该州的 <code>area_codes</code> 随机取号再格式化；若无此文件则退回内置四州区号池。</p>
    <div class="row">
      <label for="tfState">州</label>
      <select id="tfState" aria-label="州">
        <option value="AK">AK</option>
        <option value="DE" selected>DE</option>
        <option value="MT">MT</option>
        <option value="OR">OR</option>
      </select>
      <button type="button" id="btnTf">随机一条（含手机号）</button>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">合成美国地址 · generateUSAddress（可选）</h2>
    <p class="hint">该按钮需要你在 <code>data/</code> 中自备引擎合成美国地址所需的一整套 JSON；仅拷贝本仓演示包时通常会失败，属正常。</p>
    <div class="row">
      <button type="button" id="btnUs" class="secondary">generateUSAddress('DE')</button>
    </div>

    <section class="results-section" style="margin-top: 1.75rem;">
      <div class="results-header">
        <h3>生成结果（与主站同款卡片 UI）</h3>
        <button type="button" id="copy-all-btn" class="btn btn-primary">复制全部</button>
      </div>
      <div id="address-result" class="address-result empty" aria-live="polite">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p>点击上方「随机一条」或「generateUSAddress」后，结果以卡片形式显示在此，点击单格可复制。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <script type="module" src="test-harness.mjs"></script>
</body>
</html>
